l Gordillo]]\n\n===Technical staff===\n*Director of Football: Eduardo Maci\u00e1<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.realbetisbalompie.es/en/noticias/last-news/5047/eduardo-macia-conforma-la-nueva-direccion-deportiv|title=Real Betis Balompi\u00e9 - Latest News|website=www.realbetisbalompie.es|accessdate=8 June 2017|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818012133/http://www.realbetisbalompie.es/en/noticias/last-news/5047/eduardo-macia-conforma-la-nueva-direccion-deportiv|archivedate=18 August 2016}}</ref>\n*Assistant Director of Football: [[Alexis Trujillo]]\n*Head Scout: Vasiliki Pappa\n*Scouting: Jakob Friis-Hansen, [[Vlada Stosic]], Carlos Vargas, Adrian Esp\u00e1rraga and Paulo Meneses\n*Technical Analysis Department: Tino Luis Cabrera (Head) and Jaime Quesada\n*Scouting U20s: [[Juan Jos\u00e9 Ca\u00f1as]] (Head) and Pedro Morilla\n\n===Coaching staff===\n{{updated|21 May 2018}}\n*Head coach: [[Rubi (footballer)|Rubi]]\n*Assistant coach: Eder Sarabia\n*Fitness coach: Fran Soto\n*Fitness coach: Marcos \u00c1lvarez\n*Goalkeeper coach: Jon Pascua\n\n===Medical staff===\n*Head of Medical Services: Tom\u00e1s Calero\n*Physiotherapists: Fran Molano, Jos\u00e9 Manuel Pizarro, Manuel L\u00f3pez, Manuel Alcantarilla\n*Nurse: Jos\u00e9 Mar\u00eda Montiel\n\n==Honours==\n\n===Official===\n*[[La Liga]]\n**'''Winners (1):''' [[1934\u201335 La Liga|1934\u201335]]\n*[[Copa del Rey]]\n**'''Winners (2):''' [[1976\u201377 Copa del Rey|1976\u201377]], [[2004\u201305 Copa del Rey|2004\u201305]]\n**'''Runners-up (2):''' [[1931 Copa del Rey|1931]], [[1996\u201397 Copa del Rey|1996\u201397]]\n*[[Supercopa de Espa\u00f1a]]\n**'''Runners-up (1):''' [[2005 Supercopa de Espa\u00f1a|2005]]\n*[[Segunda Divisi\u00f3n]]\n**'''Winners (7):''' [[1931\u201332 Segunda Divisi\u00f3n|1931\u201332]], [[1941\u201342 Segunda Divisi\u00f3n|1941\u201342]], [[1957\u201358 Segunda Divisi\u00f3n|1957\u201358]], [[1970\u201371 Segunda Divisi\u00f3n|1970\u201371]], [[1973\u201374 Segunda Divis